Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-4通迅中断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师无法脱离机体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1 beta正向RahXephon接近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机师心脏情况异常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是控制中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救护班请立即前往373区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令，我把他带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你很意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀司令因为他的管理问题\N受到追究而被免职了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在家里闭门思过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来你就可以随意地监禁我或者处决我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出那样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你清楚你做的事的严重性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是不是MU族，我从一开始就讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是一个公正的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有利用价值我就会利用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种价值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，除了能操纵RahXephon…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人际关系都只是利益关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…会好好的利用你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了司令官，绫人才刚刚回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不打算服从我的命令的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请你和前任司令官一样暂时停职反省一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在是我的直属情报分析官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊？那个可爱的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，她是新到TERRA来的干部候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，遥少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，你好像会画画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时间的话我很想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远妹妹虽然很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的女孩也很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子！你这种行为是对久远小姐的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，她不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，就那样失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！久远小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻说她被财团保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财团啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说那个新司令官是财团的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:04:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是看错了八云少佐和紫东小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然围着那种家伙团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是彻底的背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是那种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我还在停职反省，不是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很意外，你用这种可爱的手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…我可是你的上司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，现在你不是在停职反省吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bunga mawar
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在队长祖国的语言中是蔷薇的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在这里的神名绫人就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了，怎么了？今天休息？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我申请到了有薪假期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔父呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人好像已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀，真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，你也尽心尽力了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护他的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很羡慕老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对血液的颜色之类的事好像一点也不在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样才能像老师你一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你和我们一起吃次饭就可以了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就会明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去准备饭菜收拾浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先在这里坐一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你还真的出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被TERRA的人带出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来说要让我住进相关设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说好像你住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁他们没看见的时候跑到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是TERRA？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后还发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，不少的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人，可以进来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是MU族这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…已经不再介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是鸟饲守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是紫东惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是从东京…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能对叔父保密吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会找机会和他说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时就当成我们俩之间的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了，今天我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点像浩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝比奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这边也画画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想协助神名逃跑的罪责不被追究
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以后就要忠实于我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚能陪我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是树喜欢的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是树喜欢的东西\N你总是想要弄到手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上只有两种男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种能使女人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一种则不能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊，令人厌恶之处和树一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转告总裁，计划进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上要工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是托了谁的福，现在停职反省…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子，你是那条白蛇的心腹了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我处世精明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事你都做的出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触Red
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标确认为D-1
