Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,73区，监视影像切换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白，放大倍率切换
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对D-1的行动，还未得到许可！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们究竟在干什么？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让alpha小队出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1警报发布、D-1警报发布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长，你安心地去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长，这个，我洗干净再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可以的话，一起去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点，Donnie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要“锁定”上司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie，凯西，我们要为队长努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标仍然没有行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v，12秒后与敌人接触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰，前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[D-1出现，赶快过来]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候洗澡真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定知道很多\N不为我所知道的关于绫人的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里风景真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想让浩子看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.88,0:13:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很蓝…为什么天空和大海会这么蓝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-2严重损坏，飞行员已跳伞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1 beta，来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系统开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像掉到山里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想就这样死掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你，救救我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.85,0:14:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，我很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次，一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去驾驶RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再失去任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,alpha v-3严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认奈利亚神殿内的\NRahXephon有自主意识活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…正在上升…出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！快点！开门呀！开门！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon内有生命反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎机师已经就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VERMILION
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Donnie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量水平正在无限增长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.54,0:18:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.67,0:18:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…想保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守…大家…大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.65,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底…是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力水平又上升了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去绫人会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷达反应消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有反应，好像已经撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快确认机师的生存情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是连这么点用也派不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让发生在朝比奈身上的一幕再重演了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太惨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，机师怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没得救了，头和脚都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人啊，广袤的天空和大海之所以都是蓝色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为它们都是属于蓝色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色真说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人际关系都只是利益关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是利益关系也有它自身的美学法则
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的幸福就是我的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点，他还没有意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定，他永远都不会意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么遥就会孤独一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法说出的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.77,0:23:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空，清澄透彻…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.28,0:23:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，第二十一乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Xephon的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音